# Commit authorship

- **Never** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor Agent` or any bot/AI as co-author in commit messages.
- Do not append co-author trailers to commits in this repository.
- The GitHub Action that commits EU role updates uses only `github-actions[bot]`; leave it that way.
